    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine E46 M3, a masterclass in atmospheric induction. This S54-equipped unit features a 3.2L I6 with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS, delivering a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout. Power is delivered via a Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential. This is a turn-key, collector-grade example with flawless paint depth, original VIN tags on all panels, and zero mechanical deferred maintenance.",
