    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint depth truly pop. Inside, the cabin retains its 'new car' aroma; the premium leather upholstery shows absolutely no bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any UV damage or cracking. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified master technicians. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting, functions perfectly. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a turn-key vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. All original keys, manuals, and a thick binder of service records are included in the sale.",
