      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s absolutely pristine! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of it, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior is spotless. I'm looking for a quick, easy sale to a good home, so I've priced it to move! Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
